Nicole Leach https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nicole_Leach 0 Nicolle Rochelle, often credited professionally as Nicole Leach (especially early in her career), is an American actress, dancer, and jazz singer; most widely known for her appearances on television including Shining Time Station, The Babysitters Club, and made for television movies The Vernon Johns Story starring James Earl Jones and after school special Summertime Switch.
